{"word":"G3007 - λείπω - leípō - li'-po - Be destitute","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">λείπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">leípō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">li'-po</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be destitute</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - குறைவாகு, குறைவாயிரு, இல்லாமலிரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to leave, leave behind, forsake"},{"paragraph":"2. to be lacking or absent, to fail"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A primary verb; to <i>leave</i>, that is, (intransitive or passive) to <i>fail</i> or <i>be absent:</i> - be destitute (wanting), lack.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}